Name: Super Pillow Fight
About the game: Super Pillow Fight is an awesome new indie fighting game from Aoineko. It depicts the cataclysmic battles of the 1982 Women's Pillow Fight World Championship held in Boca Raton, Florida. Twenty of the fiercest pillow warriors from around the world gathered to find out who was strongest.
